class Solution {
    public int maximumLength(String s) {
        int[][] count = new int[26][s.length() + 1];
        int left = 0;
        int n = s.length();
        int result = -1;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            while (s.charAt(left) != s.charAt(i)) {
                left++;
            }
            int target = s.charAt(i) - 'a';
            int max = i - left + 1;
            for (int j = 1; j <= max; j++) {
                count[target][j]++;
                if (count[target][j] >= 3) {
                    result = Math.max(result, j);
                }
            }
        }
        return result;
    }
}
